node.text: 'My favorite sneaker of 2021 so far, hands down, is the @maniere_usa x #AirJordan3,’ says @mad.hartman, director of social at @stadiumgoods. 'A Ma Maniére founder @james.whitner’s elevated take on the Jordan 3, a classic silhouette, puts women front and center. The combination of Whitner’s personal connection — it was the first silhouette his mom purchased for him as a kid — with luxury details creates a one-of-a-kind collab.’ Find more sneaker collabs to know now on #FARFETCH.

node.text: ‘The most exciting thing about brand collaborations is seeing brands pushed outside of their comfort zones by collaborators,’ says @mad.hartman, director of social at @stadiumgoods. 'Take a shoe like the @ambush_official x @nike #DunkHigh: the Swoosh extends past the heel which is something entirely unique to the partnership.’ Find more sneaker collabs to know now on #FARFETCH.

node.text: 'No collaborator has had a bigger impact on sneakers in the past five years than @travisscott,’ says @mad.hartman, director of social at @stadiumgoods. 'The British Khaki #AirJordan6Retro is another win from Cactus Jack, ticking several boxes that make it a must-have. 2021 is the 30th anniversary of the Air Jordan 6 and British Khaki is perfectly on trend with its neutral tones.’ Find more sneaker collabs to know now on #FARFETCH.
